    {
      "scene_index": 1,
      "label": "第一场",
      "characters_present": [
        "中军",
        "四铠将",
        "四龙套",
        "苏龙",
        "薛平贵",
        "魏虎"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四铠将、中军、苏龙、魏虎同上。〖点绛唇〗。苏龙、魏虎同归座。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一颗皇家印，令箭调三军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马踏花世界，保主定乾坤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，苏龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，魏虎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今奉圣命，扫灭西凉。\n中军过来，传令下去，击鼓听点！"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "击鼓听点！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（起鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前营！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后营！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "左营！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "右营！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先行！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？本帅初点大卯，先行因何不到？"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "披挂来迟，请元帅宽点二卯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吩咐起鼓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起鼓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（场面起鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前后营！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "左右营！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先行！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？二卯不到，其情可恼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天气炎热，请元帅宽点三卯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吩咐起鼓，单点先行。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四铠将同允。场面起鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先行！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先行！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先行！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未到！"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？本帅连点三卯，先行竟敢不到，哪里容得？来呀，将误卯牌挂出！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来在营门外，勒马下雕鞍。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵下马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见误卯牌，叫人心胆寒！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报！先行告进！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见元帅！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！本帅连点三卯，竟敢不到。你往哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "披挂来迟。望元帅恕罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "番贼前来讨战，你也披挂来迟不成？哪里容得，推出斩了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！为何将他斩首？"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他误了卯期，故而将他斩首。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斩不得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么斩不得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未曾出兵，先斩先行，于军不利！"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斩不得，我可打得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打么？嗯，但凭于你！"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来呀，两捆八十，与我打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何两捆八十？"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你也是元帅，我也是元帅，你四十，我四十，岂不是八十？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的四十不打了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你的四十不打，我是要打的。\n来呀，一捆四十，与我着实地打！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套同打薛平贵。薛平贵跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢元帅的责！"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我打得你可公？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不公！"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打得你可是？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是！"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不公也要公，不是也要是。传令下去，兵发西凉！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，兵发西凉！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四铠将同允。〖牌子〗。苏龙、魏虎、薛平贵同上马，同走圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人马撤回！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呕！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（牌子止。四龙套、四铠将分站大小边。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！今乃黄道吉日，出兵征战西凉。这样慢吞吞地行走，几时能到西凉？哪里\n容得？斩了，斩了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！又斩哪个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先行平贵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斩不得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斩不得？我还是打！来呀！两捆八十，与我打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你四十，也就够了。为何要打八十？"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还是你四十，我四十！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的四十免了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你免我不免。\n来，扯下去打！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套同打薛平贵。薛平贵跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢元帅的责！"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先行听令：吩咐三军，急急而行，往西凉去者！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！\n（薛平贵起。苏龙、魏虎、薛平贵同上马。四龙套、四铠将同下。苏龙、魏虎、薛平贵编辫子。薛平贵与魏\n虎撞，魏虎倒，薛平贵下马扶魏虎起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人马撤回！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套、四铠将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呕！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四铠将自两边分上，分站大小边。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！胆大先行，将本帅撞倒马下。哪里容得？\n来呀，与我打！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套同打薛平贵。薛平贵跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢元帅的责！"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先行听令：命你攻打头阵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "末将两腿疼痛，不能乘骑，怎能交战？"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两腿疼痛，不能乘骑，我却会治！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（魏虎拔剑威吓。薛平贵惧怕，持枪上马，下。四龙套同随下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙、魏虎",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
