      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（苏龙上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先行去交兵，未见转回程。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套引薛平贵同上。薛平贵下马，龙套甲接枪。四龙套分站两边，薛平贵进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见元帅！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。胜负如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大获全胜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本帅备酒，与先行贺功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢元帅！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套引魏虎同上，魏虎下马，进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先行回来了？攻打头阵，得胜而归。本帅营中准备酒宴，与你贺功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅抬爱，末将怎敢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "魏虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要来的，你一定要来的呀！\n来，带马回营！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（龙套戊递马鞭，魏虎上马，随四龙套同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "魏虎害我，如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有我在此，料无妨害。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "全仗元帅。\n来，带马魏营去者！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（龙套甲递马鞭，薛平贵上马，下。四龙套随苏龙同下。）"
        }
      ],
