        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。龙套戊摆酒具。魏虎劝薛平贵饮酒，薛平贵酒醉倒在桌上。）"
