      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（代金、代银同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "代金",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "代银",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "代金",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉了狼主之命，巡营瞭哨。就此前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马形驮薛平贵同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "代金",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿住奸细。"
        },
        {
          "character": "代银",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去见狼主。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（代金、代银由马上扶薛平贵下，捆。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "代金、代银",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请狼主！\n（四太监、马达、江海、代战公主、西凉王同上。四太监分站两边，马达站小边，江海、代战公主站大边，\n西凉王归座。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "西凉王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "代金、代银",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿住奸细。"
        },
        {
          "character": "西凉王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带上来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "代金、代银",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（代金、代银同下。代金、代银推薛平贵同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恼恨魏虎心太狠，\n苦苦害我命残生。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵随代金、代银同进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "看他把我怎样行！"
        },
        {
          "character": "西凉王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！胆大奸细，既已被擒，为何不跪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺乃天朝大将，岂肯跪你！"
        },
        {
          "character": "西凉王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "絮絮叨叨，哪里容得。推出斩了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（代金、代银拥薛平贵同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀下留人！\n父王，附耳上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（代战公主向西凉王作耳语。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "西凉王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "招回来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（代金、代银拥薛平贵同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要斩便斩。三番两次，你老爷好不耐烦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "西凉王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若归顺孤家，俺将女儿许配与你。你若不允，将你斩首，岂不白白送掉一条\n性命？你要再思呀再想！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵背躬。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住！可恨魏虎，苦苦害我。倒不如暂且应允。有日回朝，也好报仇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵向西凉王。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯，我应允就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "西凉王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好！与他松绑，后面更衣去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵下，更衣，上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岳父在上，受小婿大礼参拜！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵拜，起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "西凉王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想我朝又添了一员大将。招为驸马，辅佐孤王，岂不是天下无敌乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（三笑） 哈哈，哈哈，啊哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（西凉王死。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（代战公主哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
